@startuml
title Attraction Lifecycle - 3.6 (AttractionStatus)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #EEECFB
  BorderColor #8B7FD6
  FontColor #1A1A1A
  ArrowColor #444444
}
hide empty description

[*] --> DRAFT : Partner creates attraction
DRAFT --> PENDING : Partner submits for review
REJECTED --> PENDING : Partner fixes & resubmits
PENDING --> APPROVED : Admin approves\n(publishedAt set)
PENDING --> REJECTED : Admin rejects (+ reason)
APPROVED --> DRAFT : Partner edits\n(significant change)
APPROVED --> SUSPENDED : Admin hides (violation)
SUSPENDED --> APPROVED : Admin restores
DRAFT --> [*] : Partner archives
REJECTED --> [*] : Partner archives
APPROVED --> [*] : Partner archives

APPROVED : Publicly available\n(see Publication state)
@enduml
